{"tid":1038064,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"動靜脈血管畸形放射治療","createTime":"2019-02-26T11:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T18:58:43.000Z","uid":76455,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"542cd6ecdf23ea82c2a779c15ccd727f1079d3e7","tid":1038064,"uid":76455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T11:50:53.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲,有親人患左動靜脈血管畸形，曾經出左血， 醫生話個位做唔到手術， 做DSA及血管堵塞術 因為太入都做唔到，只可以做放射冶療 等啲血管自動收縮堵塞條血管。<br />\n<br />\n有沒有巴絲做放射科，知道公立用乜去做， 伽瑪刀定係xray刀，如果去私家做又可以用乜嘢方法？可唔可以用cyber 刀？係咪一樣？"},{"pid":"1fc48f3e4606adbec46a74520ee15fd23881b900","tid":1038064,"uid":76455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T14:20:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c9762d4bbebc12d9f49e7165984ad7a74c91f471","tid":1038064,"uid":216760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T14:23:08.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"0f288f27ca256a740ce867ce5b00a83ca25b715f","tid":1038064,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T16:51:58.000Z","msg":"位置呢？"},{"pid":"cb5900ccbb0a829df78fb845e9407d5c807cbd02","tid":1038064,"uid":76455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0f288f27ca256a740ce867ce5b00a83ca25b715f","tid":1038064,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T16:51:58.000Z","msg":"位置呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T12:59:08.000Z","msg":"腦內深處, 做唔到手術。剛剛book左私家做放射治療"},{"pid":"dfcbe246b8b5f779f381dc675b6baf7ffd1afeb9","tid":1038064,"uid":225998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T13:10:30.000Z","msg":"Via stereotactic radiosurgery using cyber knife"},{"pid":"b5db04638692cb0a82a8683dd097f0be3b3c914c","tid":1038064,"uid":225998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T13:15:01.000Z","msg":"Gamma knife treatment is invasive and requires LA. While cyber knife is non invasive."},{"pid":"da5239bdc1c47f308e0abfa88e1c2a99b11e187c","tid":1038064,"uid":229547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:58:43.000Z","msg":"治療AVM 所用嘅放射技術系stereotactic radiosurgery<br />\n其實用linac 傳統放射治療機 或 cyber knife（貴，精準 因為有skull b 做對位）都一樣得<br />\n兩者都係用 高能量MV X-ray 做治療<br />\n公立醫院係有得做AVM case 但<br />\n以我所知公立醫院暫時係冇cyber knife <br />\n如果想做呢個要去私家醫院 暫時最新好似cyber knife M6 (model)"}]}